title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Life, Liberty and the Pursuit of a Shape-Up
description:
A nation divided. A podcast united. Life on the brink. Throwing Fits persists. After an extended break, the Core 4 link back up on the eve of the 2020 United States presidential election—the fate of which still presumably hangs in the balance at the time of writing—to debate the fate of the country, bold predictions, Chuck’s presidential platform, Chef’s beef with his roommates, Jimmy and Larry’s rock climbing date, heading west and much more on this Patreon-exclusive boyz only edition of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
